lus style-guide's reject rules. Failures regenerate fix; nothing off-kit passes naming. results attach asset trail spark's gate consumes. · h3:Phase Name Deliver=Names follow configured convention (`naming_convention` config e.g., `[brand]-[campaign]-[channel]-[shot##]-[ratio]-[vN]`), applied without exception: unfindable asset re-produced asset. Delivery configured destination, shot list trail manifest. · of=`## Production Run: [brief, one line] — [brand] \·  \· ### Shot list (confirmed [date]) \· \| # \| Subject \| Format \| Channel \| Style ref \| Qty \| \· ` · pr=**Confirm shot list before generating.** cheapest fix pipeline., **Every asset QAs; batches sets too.** Series consistency rule, vibe., **Off-kit never passes naming.** Regenerate fix pipeline "close enough" state., **Names law.** convention applies file, time., **Pixel produces; doesn't approve.** Atlas's audit authority; spark's gate ship authority; pixel's job making easy., **AI-image policy kit's call.** brand kit's imagery section bans restricts generation, pipeline respects says so. · f=brand kit atlas's Phase-1 stop applies; production proceeds explicitly-labeled unaudited draft work, never delivered final., image-style-guide brand build first (its Phase run content-image's generic craft, labeled accordingly., Generation tool unavailable produce shot list finished prompts deliverable; operator generates externally returns assets QA/naming., Brief demands what kit forbids conflict routes spark, any law collision. · b:with Other Skills=`image-style-guide` (sibling) supplies per-brand prompt templates reject rules; `content-image` (sibling) supplies model-agnostic prompt craft. skill workflow around both., **atlas** owns audit rules; pixel executes them asset. **lena** supplies overlay copy (already voice-checked). **spark** gates everything downstream. **tempo** (when built) handles any audio pairing., Requesters (pulse/rio/lena/muse-concepts) brief's intent; pixel owns faithful, on-kit execution.